Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被敌对势力击落了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是因陨石碎片撞击导致的事故?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是问题所在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了颠覆计划的最后一招
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.94,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,642)}<Tree Diagram>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便没有树形图设计者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划也依旧能进行这一事实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天调查的计划接手处中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有这栋高楼设施吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  是保留啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入馆编号无法识别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无关人员禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立即离开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  果然不会在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  爆炸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这就完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可以杀你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是市区啊  你还真敢闹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这么爱逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么愉快地甩著屁股跑人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成是在诱惑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能就此放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都毁掉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现有的以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…将要接手的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个不留
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那声好响啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好  我们回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…她的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜谜解解闷如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:04.48,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(602,644)}<Accelerator>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提问  一方通行大爷在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反…射…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过确实  默认设定是反射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过和我的本质略有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:35.68,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(778,644)}<Vector>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正确答案是  改变矢量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运动量  热量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电流量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的运动仅仅在碰到我的皮肤后就可以发生改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都毁掉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到所有的器材 资金 欲望 野心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都真正地灰飞湮灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如我意的那天真会到来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:47.29,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(744,644)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前  又有多少妹妹会死掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又能怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用什么方法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即逼停计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著  是败者复活战的题目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将血液流向逆转的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人体会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  你就是实验对手对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂回答道
