Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂表现出自己对初战的热情道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  虽然已经被允许可以向你开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就开始第一次实验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就先下手为强了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂说完便开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹道被改变了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂拉开距离开始分析道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你他妈在逗我?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这算怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.41,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,644)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意真是超能力者的克隆体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就无视掉她和Original的性能差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过克隆体通过网络共享著记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会在两万场战斗中逐渐学习从而进化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许连你都会陷入苦战哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反过来说  我必须得一直和小卒打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扫兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次就只有她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次实验还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要处理掉身后的实验体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过处理两万个武装后的克隆体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个实验才会完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标还未停止活动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即继续进行实验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂服从命令道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处理?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止活动?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像…沉入了黑暗的深水之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:14:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂…问…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来第一次实验就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚开始或许有些无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢会变强的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请你加油来处理下咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用考虑太多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为对方只是药物和蛋白质合成的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人偶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来  去买个饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御…坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像发生案件了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  凶杀?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  还有多远
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不…这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该有尸体才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你真的看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…骗人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是做梦?  怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  哦  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近的摄像头都已经查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有录到任何可疑事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能…刚才还…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我们就报告说是目击者弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  下次我们就会联系你的学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  搞些低级的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事啊  靠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御…御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然原计划是完成工作后就回你那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂率先道歉道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是御坂妹妹  这…没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才一直以为你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂确实死亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂报告道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱著的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一  将进行密码确认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂言出必行地说道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZXC741ASD852QWE963'
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂测试道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因无法对刚才的密码进行解码
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明你不是本实验的相关人员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂下结论道
