Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂辩解道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎因本实验
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你白操心了
