Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过无须担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在场的御坂都是御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才所接触的御坂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是10032号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是我
